roduct: Clinora

Version: 1.0

Document Type: Feature Catalog & Module Breakdown

Audience: Product, Engineering, QA, DevOps, UI/UX

1. Purpose

The purpose of this document is to define every functional module and feature that will be part of the Clinora platform.

This document serves as the master inventory of the product and provides a structured view of all modules planned for the MVP and future releases.

Each feature listed here will later become:

Figma Screens
Product Requirements Documents (PRDs)
Jira Epics
Backend APIs
Database Tables
QA Test Cases
